### Sağlık kontrolü
GET http://localhost:8000/health

### 1) Fizyoterapist login
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email_or_phone": "fzt.demo@platform.local",
  "password": "Demo1234!"
}

### 2) Yeni hasta ekle (TOKEN_FZT ile)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/patients
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN_FZT}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "full_name": "Yeni Demo Hasta",
  "birth_date": "1995-09-10",
  "gender": "Kadın",
  "height_cm": 165,
  "weight_kg": 60,
  "rehab_phase": "Erken Faz",
  "email": "yeni.hasta@platform.local",
  "password": "Demo1234!"
}

### 3) Egzersiz kütüphanesini al
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/exercises/library
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN_FZT}}

### 4) Hastaya diz fleksiyon programı ata
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/exercises/programs
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN_FZT}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patient_id": "{{PATIENT_ID}}",
  "title_tr": "Diz Fleksiyon Hafta 1",
  "start_date": "2026-03-15",
  "items": [
    {
      "exercise_id": "{{EXERCISE_KNEE_FLEXION_ID}}",
      "day_of_week": 1,
      "sets": 3,
      "reps": 12,
      "hold_seconds": 1,
      "rest_seconds": 20,
      "order_no": 1
    }
  ]
}

### 5) Hasta login
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email_or_phone": "hasta.demo@platform.local",
  "password": "Demo1234!"
}

### 6) Hasta bugünkü plan
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/patients/me/today-plan
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN_PATIENT}}

### 7) Hasta seans başlat
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/exercises/sessions/start
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN_PATIENT}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patient_id": "{{PATIENT_ID}}",
  "program_item_id": "{{PROGRAM_ITEM_ID}}"
}

### 8) AI analiz - landmark ile tekrar/geri bildirim
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/ai-analysis/session-frame
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN_PATIENT}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "session_id": "{{SESSION_ID}}",
  "exercise_type": "knee_flexion",
  "landmarks": {
    "left_hip": { "x": 0.52, "y": 0.42, "z": 0, "visibility": 0.99 },
    "left_knee": { "x": 0.50, "y": 0.62, "z": 0, "visibility": 0.99 },
    "left_ankle": { "x": 0.62, "y": 0.74, "z": 0, "visibility": 0.99 }
  }
}

### 9) Ağrı günlüğü gir
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/pain-logs
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN_PATIENT}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patient_id": "{{PATIENT_ID}}",
  "pain_level": 4,
  "fatigue_level": 3,
  "stiffness_level": 2,
  "swelling_level": 1,
  "note_tr": "Egzersiz sonrası ağrım azaldı."
}

### 10) Fizyoterapist dashboard
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/physiotherapists/me/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN_FZT}}

### 11) Fizyoterapist takip ekranı - hasta follow-up
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/physiotherapists/patients/{{PATIENT_ID}}/follow-up
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN_FZT}}

### 12) Fizyoterapist - hasta ağrı logları
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/pain-logs/patient/{{PATIENT_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN_FZT}}
